<L>__{exterior tram. dawn}
<A>__{an empty tram moving through the eerie early morning streets. michael appears walking alongside it and gets on.}
<L>__{interior tram. dawn}
<A>__{michael is sitting in the second carriage. he looks up. the conductress is hanna. at first, she does not notice him. michael watches, waiting to be noticed. she turns round and looks at him. he smiles in greeting but she makes no acknowledgement at all. she turns away. he frowns, bewildered.}
